# Sales & Profit Analysis Dashboard

## Project Overview
This Power BI dashboard analyzes sales, profit, product performance, and regional trends across different countries and business segments.

## Key Insights
- Analyzed sales and profit performance across multiple countries
- Identified top-performing products and market segments
- Compared sales contribution by region and business segment
- Tracked monthly profit trends and seasonal growth patterns
- Evaluated product-wise units sold distribution

## Dashboard Features
- Interactive multi-page Power BI dashboard
- Sales & profit trend analysis
- Product and market performance insights
- Segment-wise sales distribution
- Country-level profit analysis
- Dynamic filters and slicers

## Tools & Technologies
- Power BI
- DAX
- Data Visualization
- Business Analysis

## Dataset
Financial sales dataset containing:
- Sales
- Profit
- Products
- Segments
- Countries
- Units Sold
- Targets

